[Student "S"]
{SOUTH has a poor 9 points, but does have two 4-card Majors. So he uses Stayman.

When NORTH bids \Ss, SOUTH isn't strong enough to bid game herself, so she temporizes 
with a 3\S invitation.

NORTH has a full 17 points so he accepts the invitation.}

[Event ""]
[Site ""]
[Date ""]
[Board "4"]
[Dealer "E"]
[Vulnerable "All"]
[Deal "E:KQ.AQ75.KT9.QJ84 94.T86432.7632.5 JT8765.9.AQ5.T72 A32.KJ.J84.AK963"]
[Declarer "E"]
[Contract "4S"]
[Result ""]
[Auction "E"]
