[BCFlags "1f"]
[RotationNote "Board 4, chOption: E, chBasis: N, basisKind:Declarer, nOption:1, nBasis: 0, nRot: 1, useStandardVul: true"]
[BoardVersionToken "864d958a52b8598be594c44c8c9915b5b7eabddfbbdf158eb706ca0bd2067081"]
[Category "Partnership Bidding"]
[Difficulty "intermediate"]
[SkillPath "partnership_bidding/stayman_transfers"]
[Student "S"]
{WEST, with 9 points and a 6-card suit, knows they should play in \Ss. 
The question is: how high? 

WEST transfers EAST to \Ss, then invites by raising to 3\S.

EAST has only two trumps, (good ones, admittedly), but she has a maximum 17 point hand. 
So she bids the \S game.}

